text: Habib Dallagi (born 15 January 1941) is a Tunisian former sports shooter. He competed in the 50 metre rifle, prone event at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1941 births Category:Living people Category:Tunisian male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Tunisia Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:People from Sousse
